Competition: Copa America
Season: 1925
Country: Argentina
BlockSource: http://www.rsssf.com/tables/25safull.html

* Argentina, November 29-December 25. All games played in Buenos Aires. Chile and Uruguay withdrew, Chile because of the bad performance one year ago, and Uruguay because of conflicts inside the Association. This renounces forced the organizers to modify the schedule. Finally the championship was played in two rounds.

29.11.25  Buenos Aires, Boca Juniors
ARG - PAR 2:0 (1:0)
(18,000) Ricardo Vallarino URU
ARG: Tesoriere - Bidoglio, Muttis - Médici, Vaccaro, Fortunato - Tarasconi, Sánchez,Irurieta, Seoane, Bianchi
PAR: Denis - López de Filippis, Mena Porta - Díaz, Fleitas Solich, Alvarez - Brizuela,Molinas, L.Nessi, Rivas, Fretes
1:0 Seoane 2, 2:0 Sánchez 72

06.12.25  Buenos Aires, Sportivo Barracas
BRA - PAR 5:2 (3:1)
(12,000) Gerónimo Rapossi ARG
BRA: Tuffy - Pennaforte, Clodô - Nascimento, Floriano, Fortes - Filó, Lagarto,Friedenreich, Nilo, Moderato
